                    "ryhesMouth": "close"
                },
                {
                    "text": "When he returned, he started seeing Rhyes around him. He were being haunted by him, and Rhyes is not a quiet man.",
                    "kanataMouth": "close",
                    "ryhesMouth": "close"
                },
                {
                    "text":"In the years since, he has grown acustomed to Rhyes'...company and lack of 'off switch' but Kanata has never responded to him.",
